<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Lutwyche's buyer profile is heavily influenced by the suburb's position relative to Windsor and Kelvin Grove. Buyers who have researched both sides of the price gap come to Lutwyche with a clear understanding of what they are getting: equivalent CBD proximity, comparable character housing, and meaningfully better value on the home itself. That clarity means competition on well-positioned Lutwyche properties is real when the campaign is run correctly.
