    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Lutwyche Brisbane?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Lutwyche's character home market sits at a value point relative to Windsor and Kelvin Grove, drawing buyers who want inner north proximity at a more accessible price. Properties in quieter streets away from the Lutwyche Road corridor trade at a consistent premium over apartments near the commercial strip. Contact Daniel for a current appraisal on your specific property.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Lutwyche?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented Lutwyche character homes typically sell within 30 to 48 days when priced in line with recent comparable evidence. The suburb's value position relative to Windsor and Kelvin Grove creates a consistent pool of spillover buyers who respond quickly when a correctly priced property hits the market.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Lutwyche Brisbane?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Lutwyche offers a city bus connection via Lutwyche Road, walkable access to a local shopping centre, cafes and daily retail, and character residential streets behind the commercial corridor that deliver genuine quiet. It sits five kilometres from the CBD and benefits from the amenity of Windsor and Kelvin Grove immediately to the south without carrying the same price premium. For buyers who understand the suburb beyond its main road, it is a well-connected inner north address.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What types of homes are in Lutwyche?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Lutwyche has a mix of character homes and apartments. Workers cottages, Queenslanders and post-war brick homes sit in the streets behind the Lutwyche Road corridor, while a substantial apartment and unit layer occupies the commercial strip and shopping centre precinct. Character homes in well-positioned residential streets are the primary target for owner-occupiers who have identified Lutwyche as their value entry to the inner north.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

